[section#cpp.error
    [:en] Diagnostic directive
    [:zh_CN] 诊断指令
[:en]
[%preprocessing directive[!error]]
[%preprocessing directive[!diagnostic]]
[%preprocessing directive[!warning]]
[%[`#error][%preprocessing directive[!error]]]
[:zh_CN]
[%预处理指令[!报错～]]
[%预处理指令[!诊断～]]
[%预处理指令[!警告～]]
[%[`#error][%预处理指令[!报错～]]]
]

[para]
[:en]
A preprocessing directive of either of the following forms
[:zh_CN]
如下任何形式的预处理指令

[syntax:explanation]
[`#] [`error] [~:opt pp-tokens] [~new-line]
[`#] [`warning] [~:opt pp-tokens] [~new-line]
[syntax:end]

[:en@~]
causes the implementation to produce a diagnostic message that should include the
specified sequence of preprocessing tokens; the [`# error] directive renders the
program ill-formed.
[:zh_CN@~]
导致实现产生诊断消息，其最好包含所指定的预处理记号序列；[`# error] 指令导致程序
非良构。
